episodes.title: The Cult Bar Volume 16 - Daughters of the Cult
episodes.description:
Since we had technical issues last month, we're coming back to Daughters of the Cult, a docuseries about "The Mormon Manson," Ervil LeBaron, the leader of a violent polygamist cult. 

Trigger warnings abound: violence, murder, sexual assault, food and financial control, high control group, child assault. This one really did have it all, and not in a good way.
subjects: Church of the First Born of the Lamb of God
